<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM6.10">
<l>kuṅkuma mappik kuḷircānta maṭṭittu</l>
<l>maṅkala vītivalañ ceytu maṇanī</l>
<l>raṅkava ṉōṭu muṭañceṉṟaṅ kāṉaimēl</l>
<l>mañcaṉa māṭṭak kaṉākkaṇṭēṉ tōḻīnāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O friend! I dreamt that [I] went there along with him upon an elephant,</l>
<l>Having applied saffron [and] daubed [ourselves] with cooling sandal paste;</l>
<l>circumambulated the auspicious streets rightwards,</l>
<l>and [we] were bathed with fragrant water there.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
